Month-long blueprint for “Vee AI” — built so you can actually finish it and present it tomorrow.

This is broken into 4 weeks with exact tools + what you need for each part.

### 1. Tech Stack & What You’ll Need

Core:
- Next.js 15 + Bun — frontend + API routes + admin dashboard
- Supabase — database, auth, file storage for product images. Free tier is enough
- Ollama Cloud — free AI API for WhatsApp bot. Get key at http://cloud.ollama.com
- WhatsApp Business API — use Meta WhatsApp Cloud API free for 1000 conversations/month. No phone number needed
- Flutterwave — payments for Nigeria. Test mode is free
- Hugging Face — free image generation API for outfit visuals
- Google Maps Places API — $200 free credit/month for location capture

Hosting: Vercel for http://Next.js — free. Supabase is hosted already.

### 2. System Blueprint
[Supplier] → [Next.js Admin Dashboard] → [Supabase DB]
                                              ↓
[Customer on WhatsApp] → [Ollama Cloud AI] → [API Routes] → [Supabase]
                                              ↓
                                        [Flutterwave Payment]
                                              ↓  
                                        [Logistics API / Manual]
