selling_price = supplier_base_price * 1.25
your_profit = selling_price - supplier_base_price
### 3. 4-Week Timeline

#### Week 1: Setup + Supplier Portal
Goal: Supplier can register + add products

- Set up http://Next.js project + Supabase connection
- Build /supplier/register page with Supabase Auth
- Build /supplier/products/new form: name, description, image upload, base_price, sizes, quantity
- Build /admin/products table showing all products with base_price * 1.25 calculation

Deliverable: Admin can see marked-up prices in dashboard

#### Week 2: WhatsApp AI + Product Search
Goal: AI can answer product questions

- Set up Meta WhatsApp Cloud API → get webhook URL
- Connect webhook to http://Next.js /api/whatsapp route
- Integrate Ollama Cloud: send user message → get AI response
- Build /api/products/search endpoint: AI calls this to get products from Supabase
- AI prompt: “You are a fashion assistant. Call searchProducts() when user asks for clothes. Always return price in NGN.”

Deliverable: You can message WhatsApp “show me sneakers” and AI replies with 3 products + price

#### Week 3: Smart Features + Order Flow
Goal: AI can recommend size + take order

- Build user_profiles table: shoe_size, shirt_size, height, address
- AI collects missing info: “What’s your shoe size?” → saves to Supabase
- Build /api/orders/create endpoint
- Integrate Flutterwave payment link generation
- Build image search: customer uploads photo → use Hugging Face CLIP to find similar products

Deliverable: Full flow from “I want size 42 black shoe” → AI → order created → payment link sent

#### Week 4: Enhancements + Polish
Goal: Demo-ready presentation

- Outfit generator: AI sends product image + prompt to Hugging Face SDXL → “person wearing this shirt with matching shorts”
- Google Maps: Customer shares location → AI saves coordinates to order for delivery
- Local supplier routing: Add supplier_type column. If local, show “Delivery in 2-3 days”. If dropship, show “Delivery in 14-21 days”
- Admin analytics: Simple chart of total orders + revenue

Deliverable: 5-min demo video + slide deck

