When user asks for products, call searchProducts(query). 
When user asks for price, call getPrice(productId). 
Always show price in NGN and include size recommendation based on user profile.
Outfit matching prompt:
User uploaded shirt image. Find 3 matching shorts from products table. 
Generate image prompt: "Fashionable Nigerian person wearing {shirt} with {shorts}, studio lighting"
