1. Product Overview
Problem
Nigerian online shoppers often struggle with poor product discovery, delayed customer support, and difficulty ordering
products across messaging platforms like Telegram and WhatsApp. Small suppliers also lack affordable AI-powered
storefronts and automated sales systems.
Solution
Vee AI is an AI-powered conversational commerce platform that helps customers discover products, receive
personalized recommendations, search using images or text, and place orders directly through Telegram and
WhatsApp.
The platform connects users with local and dropshipping suppliers while automating customer support, smart
recommendations, order placement, and payment processing through AI agents.
Revenue Model
• Product markup commissions (25%)
• Supplier subscription plans (future)
• Featured product promotions (future)
• Logistics partnerships (future)
2. Target Users
Customer
Nigerian shoppers using Telegram or WhatsApp who want a faster and smarter way to discover and order products
online.
Supplier
Local vendors and dropshipping suppliers who want to sell products without building their own website or managing
customer support manually.
Admin
Platform owner managing suppliers, products, AI recommendations, margins, analytics, and order operations from a
centralized dashboard.
